name: ENDURO PARADISE BALI - Dirt Bike Tour
address: Jln.Denpasar Gilimanuk, Megati, Kec. Selemadeg Tim., Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82162, Indonesia
review 1: Amazing experience! It was my fianc√©'s first time on dirt bikes and she loved it. The guys were super helpful and no one got hurt!! Highly recommend.
review 2:
Best experience on Bali from the beginning of the day when we came to Enduro paradise till the end.
For us it was first time and we scared a bit but all trip was safety, locations interesting and comfortable for both of us, instructor was always around, offered a water and took pictures and video for us.
At the end had a delicious dinner in waroung at the same place.
Spent just a perfect day.
review 3: Tabanan jungle trip with Yudi and his friend was one of my best experiences in Bali! It was my first time on a dirtbike, but the guys adapted the route to my skills and they took great care of me :). I'm sure i'll come back ;).
review 4: That was so much fun ! The track wasn't easy because of the rain but we got used to it and had good support from the instructors. Our favourite activity so far in Bali! Thanks again üòÅ
review 5: This was an awesome experience. Picked up from villa, driven to their base and fully kitted out then taken on some incredible rides from jungle to black lava fields. Can cater to all skill levels and lunch and water provided. Cant recommend these guys enough honestly you wont regret it!

name: Kebun Pak Weda
address: G3C8+H6M, Jl. Gn. Salak, Gn. Salak, Kec. Selemadeg Tim., Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82162, Indonesia
review 1: A forest farm is a sustainable agricultural system that mimics natural forests, integrating trees, shrubs, and other plants with crops and livestock. It combines elements of agroforestry, permaculture, Biodynamic and sustainable forestry using Eco Enzyme instead of Chemical fertilizer to create a diverse and resilient ecosystem. We often prioritize regenerative practices, such as minimal tillage, crop rotation, and the use of organic inputs, to enhance soil fertility and ecosystem function.
